	   <tr><td colspan=2>the 25 mana is most likely going to be better. for two reasons. wis affects your mana pool, but at lower lvls its not as apparent, so unless you are of a much higher lvl the 25 mana is going to be much better. actually at lvl 40 i'm getting about 20mana per 5 wis, so even at this lvl the wis would be the better choice. Another thing to take into account is that your wis maxes out, so if you are already 200+wis (i'm not sure what the maxes are per class and such, so this is just in general) the mana, again would be the good choice. <br><br>check out EQdruids.com for a mana per lvl chart, it's very helpful.<br>&nbsp;<br>Shareeb &lt;Veritas Arcanus&gt;<br>52 SK<br>Ulver &lt;Veritas Arcanus&gt;<br>55 Preserver<br><br>on Mith Marr</td></tr>
